HIGH-LEVEL DESIGN (HLD)
1. System Overview
Problem Definition

Customer support teams handle repetitive queries from users based on internal documentation (FAQs, manuals, policies). Manual handling leads to:

High response time
Increased operational cost
Inconsistent answers
Solution

A RAG-based Customer Support Assistant that:

Reads PDF knowledge base
Retrieves relevant information
Generates contextual answers
Escalates complex queries to humans
Scope

✔ Single PDF knowledge base (extendable)
✔ Text-based queries
✔ CLI/Web interface
✔ HITL escalation

